I am very satisfied with the service. I feel safe staying in Hanting. Breakfast is also provided. The front desk
The lady is very gentle. There are a lot of delicious food nearby. It's very clean. The newly opened ones don't have any smell. I recommend staying there.
Dear guest, thank you very much for choosing. Summer has the late glow. Just like the little guy who comes late, everyone is smiling. I love you, little guy.
